 Theodor Mashele brings us this story. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The Roodepoort Theatre is presenting a modern-day rendition of Mozart's famous masterpiece, Le Nozze di Figaro. With farce, adultery, role-playing, humour, cunning and scheming, this masterpiece offers something for everyone. The opera also addresses issues of mental health and abuse. The production is part of the first Judith Neilson Cape Town Opera Tour in 2022. * eNCA's Theodor Mashele reports.